Package: bcpredict
Title: Breast Cancer Diagnosis Predictor
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    person("Yifei", "Song", 
           email = "Yifei.Song23@student.xjtlu.edu.cn", 
           role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Predicts breast cancer diagnosis (benign vs malignant) based on 
    30 numeric features from the Wisconsin Breast Cancer Diagnostic dataset.
    Uses a trained glmnet (elastic net) model with optimized threshold for 
    classification. The package includes visualization tools for exploratory
    data analysis and model interpretation. Designed for both clinical
    researchers and machine learning practitioners.
